research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:35:+    target_objective: float = TARGET_OBJECTIVE,
research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:55:         "  如果最近 2 轮没有把 objective 明显拉低，下一轮默认优先换结构槽位，而不是继续做同 family 的局部插值。",
research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:60:         "  1. 新的 matched-objective architecture probe；优先回答新的结构槽位值不值得继续，而不是继续沿同一 family 做线性插值。",
research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:64:-        "  5. 能明显降低 exceed_alpha_0.50 的结构，即使 total_cost_ratio 有适度上升，只要 objective 更低且仍满足预算。",
research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:69:+        "  7. 能明显降低 exceed_alpha_0.50 的结构，即使 total_cost_ratio 有适度上升，只要 objective 更低且仍满足预算。",
research/history/patches/round_0248.patch:74:         "  1. 只改善 FVU、却没有改善 objective_score 的局部 recipe 微调。",
