research/history/logs/agent_action_0144.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i 是 shared low-rank coarse stage 的重构，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”是否能在约 0.30x total_cost 下优于当前刚形成的新 lowrank+expert 低成本锚点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.30x 下明显优于 r143，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，继续定位 coarse/residual 的低成本分工边界。","如果结果只与 r143 接近，则说明把 trunk 从全局 lowrank 改成 shared low-rank coarse stage 的结构收益有限，后续可优先转向带全局 residual 的三段式结构，而不是继续打磨这条两段式线。","如果新 family 明显劣于 r143，则可以更明确地把当前 low-cost 主线保留在 `lowrank_expert_topk`，同时下调 shared-lowrank two-stage 方向优先级。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，真实改动仅在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","按 `sae-architecture-integration` 做了 exact architecture smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 已可 instantiate/forward/backward。","成本自检：selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":143,"self_review":"这轮满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r143 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 刚形成新低成本 anchor 之后，继续在其内部做局部扫参会过早收缩搜索空间；新增一个最小可运行的两段式原型 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，更符合当前阶段对“shared experts + routed experts / two-stage residual expert”结构槽位的补证据需求。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是用 shared low-rank coarse stage 替代 full lowrank trunk 可能损失一部分全局主干表达，但这正是本轮要验证的结构问题。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`：用 shared low-rank coarse stage 先做第一段重构，再让 expert residual stage 处理剩余结构。建议本轮以 r143 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，直接测试这条新的两段式 hetero MoE 结构能否在约 0.30x total_cost 下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0140.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"256"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库；在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 两个小 expert 子库查表 + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 仍判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 320 降到 256，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，在不再削掉第二个 routed expert 的前提下，直接测试“更小 expert 子库 + residual cleanup”能否把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.56x，同时显著优于 r139 的单 expert 失败点并尽量接近 r138 的质量锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256` 仍接近 r138 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 进一步压 shared scorer，继续向 0.5x 靠近。","如果该点明显好于 r139 但仍被 r138 支配，则可初步判定这条线更敏感的是 active expert 数而不是 per-expert width；后续优先做更温和的 expert 容量压缩而不是再削 active path。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256` 也明显掉点，则说明当前 residual cleanup 还不足以支撑更小 routed 子库，这条 family 在 >0.5x 带的可压缩空间可能有限，下一轮应优先切回别的结构槽位而不是继续沿同一 family 深挖。"],"notes_to_memory":["r139 已给出清晰负信号：`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 会把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 FVU 从 0.0946 拉回到 0.1511，因此后续压缩应优先保持双 expert 激活路径。","本地 allowlist 自检通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual')` 接受 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`，不会在训练前被判为 `Disallowed env override keys`。","成本自检：在 r138 配方下把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 设为 256 后，selection_accesses=1830912、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=2355200，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.56，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":138,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r138 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。r139 已经把“减少 active experts”这条低成本方向回答得很清楚，再继续在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 上打磨信息增量不高；改为缩小 per-expert 子库更符合当前阶段对“expert 更小、router 仍轻、总激活路径不膨胀”的要求，也比回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参更贴合当前 hetero MoE 议程。主要风险是 expert 子库一旦缩小，质量仍可能快速回退；但这正是当前最需要确认的结构边界。","summary":"建议以 r138 为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`。这是一轮针对 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 matched-cost expert 缩容探针：保持双 routed expert 不变，直接回答“更小 expert 子库 + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.56x total_cost 下保住 r138 的大部分质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0239.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = t(x) + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈Ŝ_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是静态 low-rank trunk 库 U={u_r} 的重构，{b_{e,i}} 是静态 expert 子库原子，E(·) 由轻量 router 选出的少量 experts，expert 内系数改为 JumpReLU 形式 α_{e,i}(x)=ReLU(z_{e,i})·σ((ReLU(z_{e,i})-τ_{e,i})/bandwidth)·p_e(x)。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的链路仍是“trunk 查表/加权和 -> router 选少量静态 expert 子库 -> 子库内 JumpReLU-gated sparse support -> 有限加权和”，没有动态生成字典，因此 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` 判断为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮主假设是：r238 已经说明 variable-active-path 在 same-cost K=32 lane 上没有收益，而当前又已连续两轮无改进，应切到新的结构槽位；相对 r235 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到新实现的 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=16, NUM_EXPERTS=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192, adam, LR=8e-4` 不变，直接测试“shared low-rank trunk + routed JumpReLU experts”是否能在约 total_cost_ratio=0.19140625 这一带用更强的主干/tail 分工换回明显更低的 exceed_alpha_0.50。","summary":"已实际落盘最小新 family `lowrank_expert_jumprelu`，并补齐 whitelist、factory dispatch 与 override wiring。建议以 r235 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_jumprelu`，做一轮新的 low-rank-trunk 结构 probe；本地 smoke、成本复核和 allowlist 校验均已通过。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"lowrank_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮没有继续围绕 `expert_jumprelu` 做低信息细扫，而是按当前状态 `consecutive_no_improve=2` 切到新的结构槽位，符合主线策略。选择 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` 而不是 `lowrank_expert_residual`，因为本地精确成本复核显示前者 combined_accesses=802816、total_cost_ratio=0.19140625，仍在当前优先的 0.14x-0.20x 带；后者会直接到 0.44x，信息密度太低。该 family 与现有实现的精确差异不是重命名：它把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 expert-local top-k 支撑换成 `expert_jumprelu` 式平滑门控，从而测试 trunk 是否能让 small-K 路线的 exceed 退化更慢。主要风险也很明确：要在 0.1914x 成本下击败当前 incumbent 0.35449，需要 exceed 压到约 0.1631 以下，这个门槛不低；如果这轮仍做不到，就应快速下调这条 lowrank+JumpReLU 结构线，而不是继续补局部插值。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已新增并注册 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu`；真实代码改动落在 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","`lowrank_expert_jumprelu` 的语义是“static low-rank trunk + routed static expert sublibraries + expert-local JumpReLU gating”；按 LUTurbo 约束判断应归为扩展兼容，而不是不兼容 family。","exact architecture smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=128, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=192, trunk_rank=16)` 可在本地成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 exact 成本复核：`lowrank_expert_jumprelu K=32 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=16 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 的 selection_accesses=557056、deployment_accesses=245760、combined_accesses=802816、exact total_cost_ratio=0.19140625，和 `lowrank_expert_topk` 同成本。","override allowlist 已接通：`validate_env_overrides` 对 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_jumprelu` 以及其 `TRUNK_RANK/NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 组合均返回空列表。","r238 `adaptive_active_expert_jumprelu` 在 same-cost K=32 lane 上 objective=0.360480、exceed=0.196417，说明最小 Expert-Choice-like 变体暂时不值得继续主线推进。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu@K32` 明显压低 exceed，哪怕 objective 还未击败 incumbent，下一轮优先保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向左探一个更低 encoder-cost 的点，测试 trunk 是否可更便宜地保留该 exceed 收益。","如果这轮在 0.1914x 成本下仍无法把 exceed 压到大约 0.17 以内，则应快速归档这条 lowrank+JumpReLU 线，转去更不对称的 shared/coarse + routed residual family，而不是继续在该 family 上补 K 或阈值细扫。","如果该 family 明显优于同成本 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则后续才值得在同 family 内做单变量 knee 搜索；否则只保留为历史参考，不进入兼容主线 leaderboard 的推进依据。"],"reference_round":235}
