research/history/logs/agent_action_0178.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是由共享低秩分支导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧只做 shared bottleneck 打分、轻量 router 选择少量 experts，并在静态 shared/expert 子库上做有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能保留为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。r176 已确认 routed-only `expert_topk` 在当前 `K=108, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的轻 active-path recipe 下明显弱于 low-cost anchors，r177 又确认 fully factorized hetero-MoE 更差；因此当前更高信息量的问题是：问题到底在于“缺 shared branch”，还是在于“hetero/shared 方向整体不值得继续”。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“shared bottleneck + expert-specific full heads”这条高优先级结构槽位是否能在近低成本带提供比 routed-only 与 fully-factorized 更有价值的证据。本地成本自检显示该候选在当前 1024x4096 proxy 下 selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对应 combined_ratio 约 `0.26x`，虽然略高于主战场上沿，但仍明确处于允许的 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内，也显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 `0.26x` 下明显优于 r176 的 routed-only `expert_topk`，并接近或优于它自己历史上的低成本结果，则说明 shared branch 仍有结构价值；下一轮可保持该 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `K=112`，确认它在低成本辅助带的 deployment knee。","如果该点仍明显弱于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，且也没有优于 r176/r177 的结构对照，则可更明确地下调当前 target 上 `shared bottleneck + expert-specific head` 这条 hetero-MoE 分支优先级，转向其他尚未充分证伪的 very-light residual / factorized 方向。"],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式应继续按 `扩展兼容` 处理：静态 shared 低秩库加静态 routed expert 子库上的有限加权和。","最近三轮 low-cost architecture probes 已给出更清晰的结构归因：r176 说明去掉 shared branch 的 routed-only `expert_topk` 明显偏弱，r177 说明把 hetero shared+routed 两端都 factorize 会更差。","本轮是一个 architecture-level matched-cost probe，不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线内补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值。","本地成本自检：在 r165 的 recipe 上切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 total_cost 约 `0.26x`，处于当前允许的辅助对照带。"],"reference_round":165,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然该点略高于 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近三轮已经连续排除了 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，当前最需要的是用一个仍在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内的高优先级结构槽位，把“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”这条线做一次更干净的 matched validation。选择它而不是继续回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，是因为前者已有更强负信号，后者又属于当前已明确下调优先级的 two-stage/hetero residual 方向。主要风险是该 family 在 r172/r174 已有偏弱结果；但这次是以当前更相关的 r165 low-cost anchor recipe 做 fresh matched probe，结论会更直接。","summary":"以 r165 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，做一轮 `0.26x` 左右的辅助带 architecture probe。目标是直接回答：在当前 low-cost anchor recipe 下，把 shared 分支改成更轻的 low-rank bottleneck、同时保留 expert-specific full heads，是否比 routed-only 或 fully-factorized 方向更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0232.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_m γ_m(r(x)) c_m`，其中 `h(x)=Bx` 是共享低维 bottleneck，`U={u_i}` 是 shared low-rank 静态库，`{B_e}` 是 routed expert 静态子库，`C={c_m}` 是 residual 静态补偿库，`r(x)` 是 shared+routed 重构后的残差。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank 投影 + shared/routed 子库查表 + residual cleanup 查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性在线补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等仍属兼容 family；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：Round 229 与 Round 230 已证明 residual cleanup 确实能显著降低 exceed，而 Round 231 又证明 factorized shared+routed residual 过轻，守不住这部分收益；因此当前最高信息量问题是，更强但仍低维的 shared low-rank 路径是否能保住 cleanup 收益。相对 r212 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接裁决“shared low-rank trunk + routed residual experts”这条更强 shared 路径本身值不值得继续。本地精确成本复核显示该点 selection_accesses=1785856、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=1949696，对当前 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.46484375；若要刷新 r212 的 objective=0.35553750753402713，需要 exceed_alpha_0.50 压到约 `≤-0.10930624246597288`，这在数学上已不现实。因此这不是近端翻盘点，而是一轮结构裁决：如果它仍无法把 exceed 明显压到优于 r229/r230 的档位，则 shared-lowrank residual 线在当前 target 上也应整体降级。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual@K32` 的 exceed 仍不优于 Round 229 的 `0.160599`，则说明更强 shared low-rank 路径也无法换回足够大的 cleanup 收益；后续应整体下调这条 family，而不是继续补 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或相关近邻插值。","如果该 probe 的 exceed 介于 Round 229 与 Round 230 之间，说明 shared low-rank 路径确有一定价值但交换率不足；后续只应把这条线保留为高质量历史参考，而不应继续主导预算。","如果该 probe 意外把 exceed 压到明显低于 `0.15`，则说明更强 shared path 的确重要；下一轮才值得在该 family 内继续做单参数 follow-up，但那应当发生在允许回到 param-only 压缩轴时。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 229 `lowrank_expert_residual@K32` 给出 `objective=0.602006 / cost=0.441406x / exceed=0.160599 / fvu=0.134527`，说明 trunk + routed expert + residual cleanup 能明显压低 exceed，但 objective 交换率很差。","Round 230 `two_stage_residual_expert@K32` 给出 `objective=0.586051 / cost=0.414062x / exceed=0.171988 / fvu=0.146965`，说明去掉 trunk 后 cleanup 收益仍在，但不如 `lowrank_expert_residual`。","Round 231 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual@K32` 给出 `objective=0.698899 / cost=0.394531x / exceed=0.304368 / fvu=0.260040`，说明 factorized shared+routed residual 过轻，完全守不住 cleanup 收益。","本轮选择 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的原因是：在 remaining compatible families 里，它最直接回答“更强 shared low-rank 路径是否比 factorized shared+routed 更能保住 residual-cleanup 收益”这一当前最高信息量问题。","本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual}], fallback_architecture='expert_topk')` 返回空列表。","本地成本复核：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual K=32 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.46484375，其中 selection=0.42578125x、deployment=0.0390625x。"],"reference_round":212,"self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r212 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，没有新增参数，也没有代码改动。没有再选 `whitened_topk`、`codebook_topk`、`routed`、`bucketed_topk` 等 remaining family，因为它们与当前 residual-cleanup 归因问题相比信息增量更低，而且都不具备现实 objective 赢面。也没有回到已经被 current-target 明确裁掉的 single-library selector、factorized selector 或 simple shared+routed 线。选择 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的风险同样明确：它不可能刷新 incumbent，因此只能作为结构裁决，而不是 frontier attack；但在 Round 229-231 之后，这正是当前 remaining search space 里最值得回答的问题。","summary":"建议以 r212 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`。这轮的目的不是直接冲击 incumbent，而是判断 residual-cleanup 的收益是否需要更强的 shared low-rank 路径才能保住，从而决定这条结构线是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
