research/history/round_summaries/round_0110.json:42:      "如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288` 劣于 r109 明显，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 低成本线更缺 encoder 宽度而不是 lookup budget，后续不应继续压每-expert width，而应转向 `K`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0097.json:36:      "当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴还缺少 `K=112` 这一中间点；补齐它比立即切去 `lowrank_expert_residual` 更符合 Round 97 的 runtime priority。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0097.json:41:      "如果 `K=112` 形成新的非支配中间点，则 `K=96-128` 边界已基本完成，下一轮应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 结构对照，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上细扫。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0097.json:42:      "如果 `K=112` 基本贴着 r95-r96 的平滑插值且不形成新前沿，则说明当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 已足够清楚；下一轮同样应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0101.json:99:      "如果该原型无明显收益，说明共享容量本身不足以替代 trunk/residual，后续应把 shared+routed 只作为 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的附加分支而不是独立主线。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0101.json:121:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0106.json:41:      "如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 只带来很小改善或变差，则可初步判断当前 shared+routed 收益更依赖单 expert 宽度而非多 routed experts，后续应收缩这条 family，把低成本预算转回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0137.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e*(x)}(x)} α_i(x) b_{e*(x),i}，也可写成 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} 1[e=e*(x)] α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“轻量 router 选 1 个静态 expert 子库 -> 子库内 local top-k -> 静态向量查表加权和”；静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 仍是直接兼容。`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 等属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，只能保留历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。主假设：r136 的 routed-only 失败主要来自显式 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` 后默认 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 膨胀到 1024，导致 expert 不再“小而轻”；若只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 压回 320，保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 `K=128` 不变，就能把该 family 重新放回“router 轻、expert 更小、激活路径短”的有效 MoE-like 区间，并以约 0.23x total_cost 重新回答 routed-only 是否值得保留。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0233.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ee1\u8db3\u5f53\u524d round-233 \u7684 matched architecture probe \u7ea6\u675f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684\u5b8c\u6574\u914d\u7f6e\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u53d8 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff1b`K`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR`\u3001`OPTIMIZER`\u3001`LR` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u90fd\u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ece\u73b0\u6709\u5df2\u6ce8\u518c family \u4e2d\u6311 probe\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u524d `K=32` matched lane \u4e0a\u7684 `lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`factorized_topk`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4e3b\u8981\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u90fd\u5df2\u7ed9\u51fa\u660e\u786e\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u800c\u5269\u4f59\u672a\u95ed\u5408 family \u7684 exact cost \u5927\u591a\u5df2\u8fdc\u79bb `0.18x~0.22x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u3002\u65b0 family \u7684\u5de5\u7a0b\u6539\u52a8\u88ab\u63a7\u5236\u5728 `sparsify/`\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u5f15\u5165\u65b0\u53c2\u6570\u63a5\u7ebf\u98ce\u9669\uff1b\u540c\u65f6\u5b83\u6b63\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684\u201c\u66f4\u8f7b scorer / router\u201d\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u4f46\u6bd4 `factorized_expert_topk` \u66f4\u4fdd\u5b88\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u53ea\u4f4e\u79e9\u5316 router\u3001\u4fdd\u7559 full expert heads\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f router \u538b\u7f29\u4ecd\u53ef\u80fd\u7834\u574f expert \u9009\u62e9\u8d28\u91cf\uff1b\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u8fde\u8fd9\u79cd\u6700\u5c0f\u4fb5\u5165\u7684 router-only \u4f4e\u79e9\u5316\u90fd\u5b88\u4e0d\u4f4f exceed\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u679c\u65ad\u5730\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761\u65b9\u5411\u7684\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002",
