research/history/round_summaries/round_0060.json:41:      "如果 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 改善仍很弱，则可较清晰判定 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的短板不只是 trunk 宽度，后续应把预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`，而不是继续在这条 family 上加容量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0109.json:42:      "如果 `K=96` 明显劣于当前 shared+routed 点，则可初步判断这条结构线在当前 target 上更缺局部 lookup budget 而非 encoder 宽度，后续应保持 `K=128`，再评估 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288/352` 或切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0113.json:41:      "如果 `K=64` 相比 r112 明显劣化并失去非支配性，则说明当前 shared+routed 线已接近 deployment knee；下一轮不应继续降 K，而应改做 matched `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1/3` 或切回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 做对照。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0084.json:18:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，且 |E(x)| = ACTIVE_EXPERTS 很小。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 少量 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 仍属扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。最近 r82 与 r83 已给出清晰负信号：现有单-expert 路由下，单纯压粗 expert 粒度在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `lowrank_expert_residual` 都会退化。这说明当前真正未验证的高优先级问题已不再是旧轴微调，而是提示里反复强调的“总容量与 active path 解耦”是否值得做最小原型。因此本轮不再继续 param_only 细扫，而是对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 增加新 tunable `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，并以 r60 为参考做第一轮接线验证：只新增 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，保持 `K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，验证 shared trunk + 2-expert routed lookup 是否能在总 active path 仍短的前提下改善质量。首轮目标不是宣称新前沿，而是先确保 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint config 中都真实出现 `active_experts=2`，并拿到第一条兼容、可计成本、可导出的 MoE-like 证据。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0084.json:24:    "self_review": "这轮故意不再做 `param_only`，因为最近连续七轮已经把当前已实现 family 的主要低成本旧轴基本扫清：`lowrank_expert_residual` 上提高 `STAGE1_RATIO`、压 `TRUNK_RANK`、压粗 `NUM_EXPERTS` 都退化，`lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 改到 16/64 也都不优于 32，`two_stage_residual_expert` 的 matched probe 也明显偏弱。继续在这些轴上细扫的信息增量已经很低。相反，提示里明确要求把预算转向真正的 MoE-like 稀疏扩容，并优先补 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 这类能把总容量与 active path 解耦的 tunable。本轮只新增一个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，并把接线范围限制在 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/` 和 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`，符合约束。主要风险是首轮更多是在做工程接线与可导出性验证，数值可能不会立刻优于 frontier；但这是当前最必要的最小原型步骤，否则后续搜索会继续被单-expert 旧结构困住。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0084.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮故意不再做 `param_only`，因为最近连续七轮已经把当前已实现 family 的主要低成本旧轴基本扫清：`lowrank_expert_residual` 上提高 `STAGE1_RATIO`、压 `TRUNK_RANK`、压粗 `NUM_EXPERTS` 都退化，`lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 改到 16/64 也都不优于 32，`two_stage_residual_expert` 的 matched probe 也明显偏弱。继续在这些轴上细扫的信息增量已经很低。相反，提示里明确要求把预算转向真正的 MoE-like 稀疏扩容，并优先补 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 这类能把总容量与 active path 解耦的 tunable。本轮只新增一个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，并把接线范围限制在 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/` 和 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`，符合约束。主要风险是首轮更多是在做工程接线与可导出性验证，数值可能不会立刻优于 frontier；但这是当前最必要的最小原型步骤，否则后续搜索会继续被单-expert 旧结构困住。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0230.json:7:  "family_name": "two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0230.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `two_stage_residual_expert`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_1(x)} \u03b1_i(x) b_i + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} \u03b3_{e,j}(r_1) c_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `r_1 = x - \u03a3_{i\u2208S_1(x)} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c`B={b_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 coarse/stage-1 \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{C_e}` \u662f routed residual expert \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201ccoarse \u67e5\u8868 + residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u5c5e\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1aRound 229 \u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual@K32` \u867d\u7136 objective \u5f88\u5dee\uff0c\u4f46\u9996\u6b21\u628a `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u660e\u663e\u538b\u5230 `0.160599`\uff0c\u8fd9\u4f7f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u4ece\u201c\u8fd9\u6761\u7ebf\u80fd\u4e0d\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u8d62\u201d\u8f6c\u4e3a\u201c\u8fd9\u4e00\u6536\u76ca\u5230\u5e95\u6765\u81ea low-rank trunk\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u6765\u81ea\u4e0d\u5bf9\u79f0 coarse + residual-expert cleanup \u5206\u5de5\u672c\u8eab\u201d\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u88c1\u51b3 trunk \u662f\u5426\u662f\u62ff\u5230\u4f4e exceed \u7684\u5fc5\u8981\u7ec4\u6210\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1572864\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=1736704\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.4140625\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 r212 \u7684 objective=0.35553750753402713\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u2264-0.05852499246597288`\uff0c\u8fd9\u5728\u6570\u5b66\u4e0a\u5df2\u4e0d\u73b0\u5b9e\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u540c\u6837\u4e0d\u662f\u8fd1\u7aef\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u7ed3\u6784\u5f52\u56e0 probe\uff1a\u5982\u679c\u53bb\u6389 trunk \u540e exceed \u4ecd\u63a5\u8fd1 r229\uff0c\u5219 trunk \u4ef7\u503c\u88ab\u9ad8\u4f30\uff1b\u82e5 exceed \u660e\u663e\u56de\u5347\uff0c\u5219 trunk \u7684\u786e\u662f\u5f53\u524d tail-error \u63a7\u5236\u7684\u5173\u952e\u6765\u6e90\u3002",
