research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式：x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 为 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 为 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 为全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性 residual 补偿 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r146 只把 ARCHITECTURE 从 lowrank_expert_residual 切到 shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual，保持 K=112、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、NUM_EXPERTS=64、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变，做一次 matched-cost 结构对照，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed expert + residual”在约 0.55x total_cost 下是否比当前 trunk-based lowrank_expert_residual 更值得继续。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:20:    "summary": "建议基于 r146 做一次 matched-cost architecture swap：仅设置 ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual。它是 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，且在当前 K=112/EF=1 recipe 下本地估算总成本约 0.55x，正好回答当前最需要的结构问题：shared low-rank basis + routed expert + residual，是否比 trunk-based lowrank_expert_residual 更能形成新的中成本 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r146 只改 ARCHITECTURE。当前高优先级问题是异构 MoE 的 shared+basis 版本在加入 residual 后是否还能成立；无 residual 的 shared-lowrank 线在 r141/r144 已给出较弱信号，但 shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual 早先在更高 K/更宽 expert 配方上出现过一次 keep，因此值得在当前更压缩、且与 r146 近同成本的 recipe 上做干净复验。风险是该 family 仍可能被 r146 直接压制；但即使失败，也能更明确地终止一条当前 agenda 中仍悬而未决的 hetero-MoE residual 方向。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0147.json:30:        "value": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"
