research/history/round_summaries/round_0239.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_jumprelu` \u505a\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001 `consecutive_no_improve=2` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u7b26\u5408\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7b56\u7565\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u524d\u8005 combined_accesses=802816\u3001total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7684 0.14x-0.20x \u5e26\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u5230 0.44x\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u5bc6\u5ea6\u592a\u4f4e\u3002\u8be5 family \u4e0e\u73b0\u6709\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff1a\u5b83\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 expert-local top-k \u652f\u6491\u6362\u6210 `expert_jumprelu` \u5f0f\u5e73\u6ed1\u95e8\u63a7\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6d4b\u8bd5 trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 small-K \u8def\u7ebf\u7684 exceed \u9000\u5316\u66f4\u6162\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u4e5f\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u8981\u5728 0.1914x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.35449\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1631 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4ecd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u5c31\u5e94\u5feb\u901f\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761 lowrank+JumpReLU \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0239.json:78:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_jumprelu` \u505a\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001 `consecutive_no_improve=2` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u7b26\u5408\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7b56\u7565\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u524d\u8005 combined_accesses=802816\u3001total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7684 0.14x-0.20x \u5e26\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u5230 0.44x\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u5bc6\u5ea6\u592a\u4f4e\u3002\u8be5 family \u4e0e\u73b0\u6709\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff1a\u5b83\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 expert-local top-k \u652f\u6491\u6362\u6210 `expert_jumprelu` \u5f0f\u5e73\u6ed1\u95e8\u63a7\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6d4b\u8bd5 trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 small-K \u8def\u7ebf\u7684 exceed \u9000\u5316\u66f4\u6162\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u4e5f\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u8981\u5728 0.1914x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.35449\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1631 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4ecd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u5c31\u5e94\u5feb\u901f\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761 lowrank+JumpReLU \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0074.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r73 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 64 提到 128，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，继续回答当前低成本带最关键的问题：如果 r73 的改善来自 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容仍未吃满，而不是偶然训练波动，那么进一步放大总静态 expert 容量、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 和相同查表路径长度，应能在近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并把这条直接兼容的 routed-only 前沿继续向下推进。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0074.json:42:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` 改善很弱或停止，则可较清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在总子库容量，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这类带 shared basis / residual cleanup 的兼容方向。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0103.json:86:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0128.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做局部邻域延长，符合当前运行时优先级；也不新增 env key，因此无需改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择 r108 而不是更近的 r121-r123，是因为 r108 提供了当前新 family 最干净的 matched shared+routed recipe，且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, K=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已被证明是可行的强基线。主要风险是 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 shared basis 可能损失过多表达能力；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0128.json:64:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做局部邻域延长，符合当前运行时优先级；也不新增 env key，因此无需改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择 r108 而不是更近的 r121-r123，是因为 r108 提供了当前新 family 最干净的 matched shared+routed recipe，且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, K=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已被证明是可行的强基线。主要风险是 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 shared basis 可能损失过多表达能力；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:20:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库，x_stage1 为 shared+routed stage 的重构。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，利用 residual cleanup 吃掉少掉的第二个 routed expert 覆盖，从而把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x，同时尽量保住 r138 的 FVU=0.0946，回答这条 hetero MoE + residual 线能否在 0.5x 左右形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:21:    "summary": "已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的参数接线 blocker，使该新 family 后续可以合法做单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r138 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，直接测试“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert + residual cleanup”能否把这条 hetero MoE 线从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x total_cost，并保持足够接近 r138 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:24:    "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:26:    "self_review": "先修真实 blocker，再发实验：r138 已证明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 有结构价值，但此前它没有接入 family-specific override allowlist，后续任何合法的单变量 param-only 探针都会在训练前被判为 disallowed。当前已实际补上该 wiring，并做了本地 allowlist 自检。计划运行时相对 r138 只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则；风险是第二个 routed expert 仍对当前 target 很关键，导致 FVU 回退，但这会直接回答 residual stage 是否足以支撑更轻的 expert 激活路径。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0139.json:38:      "已实际落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist，真实改动仅在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。",
